decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing the aggressive playstyle of partner commanders Jeska and Kraum to quickly overwhelm opponents. With a mix of efficient removal spells, countermagic, and powerful creatures, the deck aims to put pressure on the opponent early and maintain tempo throughout the game. By curving out with threats like Delver of Secrets and Dragon's Rage Channeler, while disrupting the opponent's game plan with cards like Force of Will and Counterspell, the deck looks to close out games swiftly. Additionally, cards like True-Name Nemesis and Vendilion Clique provide resilient threats that can be difficult for opponents to deal with. Overall, the deck aims to be proactive and proactive in its game plan, utilizing a mix of aggression and disruption to secure victories.
